[
  {
    "component": "Section",
    "data": [
      {
        "component": "Heading",
        "type": "h1",
        "text": {
          "en": "Motion",
          "jp": "モーション"
        }
      },
      {
        "component": "Text",
        "type": "lead",
        "text": {
          "en": "Motion shows the organization of a product (desktop & mobile websites, native apps, etc.) and what the product can do. The entire UI is driven by motion - it adds a whole new level of depth to the interaction design that redefines the navigation and creates a more natural experience.",
          "jp": "モーションは、サイトとアプリの体系と機能を端的に示します。モーションはUI全体をドライブし、インタラクションに新しい次元の深みを加え、ナビゲーションを再定義し、より自然な体験を作り出します。"
        }
      },
      {
        "component": "Text",
        "type": "",
        "text": {
          "en": "Possibly the most important thing that motion can bring is ‘delight’. Injecting subtle motion into design can make users feel like they are interacting with something that has a personality, thus ultimately contributing towards a truly delightful and memorable user experience.",
          "jp": "モーションの最も重要な側面は、“喜び”をもたらすことです。細かなモーションをデザインに加えると、ユーザーは個性あるものと交流しているイメージを抱き、嬉しく印象に残る体験をしていると思います。"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "component": "Section",
    "data": [
      {
        "component": "Text",
        "type": "",
        "text": {
          "en": "Motion can also:",
          "jp": "モーションによって、下記を実現できます"
        }
      },
      {
        "component": "List",
        "type": "",
        "list": {
          "en": [
            {
              "text": "Reflect the Rakuten brand personality"
            },
            {
              "text": "Draw attention to a specific area or help to distract from it"
            },
            {
              "text": "Control the transitions of hierarchy at each moment in time"
            },
            {
              "text": "Make the UI more predictable and easier to navigate by putting emphasis on the right elements"
            },
            {
              "text": "Provide clues as to what is about to happen, reinforcing the actions a user is performing, and filling the spatial relationships between screens and elements"
            }
          ],
          "jp": [
            {
              "text": "楽天ブランドの個性を反映できます"
            },
            {
              "text": "特定の箇所に注意を引く、または注意をそらすことができます"
            },
            {
              "text": "階層関係のある遷移をコントロールできます"
            },
            {
              "text": "適切な要素を強調することで、UIをより予測可能にナビゲートしやすいものにできます"
            },
            {
              "text": "状況判断を容易にし、ユーザーが実行しているアクションを明確にし、画面と要素の関係を補足します"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  {
    "component": "Section",
    "data": [
      {
        "component": "Heading",
        "type": "h3",
        "text": {
          "en": "Types of motion",
          "jp": "モーションのタイプ"
        }
      },
      {
        "component": "Row",
        "data": [
          {
            "component": "Column",
            "className": "motion-img",
            "cols": "6",
            "data": [
              {
                "component": "Heading",
                "type": "h4",
                "text": {
                  "en": "Transitions",
                  "jp": "トランジション"
                }
              },
              {
                "component": "SquareFrame",
                "data": [
                  {
                    "component": "Image",
                    "type": "",
                    "responsive": true,
                    "src": {
